title: Rare! 2-bed down unit in desirable Westpark w/parking; Avail 10/1
map_address: 3275 Rocky River Drive near Edgecliff & Munn Avenues
posting_body: ['Downstairs, first-floor unit of a high-quality, two-family home.', 'Professionally updated and recently remodeled!', 'Beautifully maintained.', 'Tasteful paint colors, clean carpeting, newer windows, real wood blinds, A/C, solid brick exterior.', 'Two bedrooms plus one extra bonus room (office, study, den, TV/reading room, playroom), living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen, one full bathroom.', 'All kitchen appliances stay, including dishwasher.', 'Loads of storage.', 'Full basement rec room with your own newer, non-shared washer and dryer in basement.', 'Deep manicured back yard with deck.', 'Detached garage parking for 1 spot with electric door opener.', "Wonderful location in highly desirable West Park neighborhood near Kamm's Shopping Plaza, Fairview Hospital, schools (Our Lady of Angels, St. Joseph's Academy, St. Mark's), airport, I-90, Lakewood, Rocky River, and Metroparks.", 'Also close to several churches and libraries.', 'Tenant responsible for all utilities, including water and sewer.', 'ABSOLUTELY NO PETS (only exception: service animal).', 'NO SMOKING.', 'Sorry, no Section 8 vouchers.', 'Minimum credit score: 675.', 'Subject to background check.', "First month's rent, last month's rent, and security deposit all due upon signing.", 'Tours by appointment only.', 'Available October 1!']
